Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-[birds chirping]\N-[theme music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Hilda ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[woman vocalizing]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[David whimpers]\NI hate dark, creepy tunnels.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They tend to be filled\Nwith things that are horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.39,0:00:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be thanking me\Nwhen we get our Sparrow Scout badges
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.93,0:01:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,for subterranean urban exploration.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a real badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.52,0:01:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet, but Raven Leader\Nwill be so impressed with us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.19,0:01:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that she'll have no choice\Nbut to create one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.15,0:01:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be the first Sparrow Scouts\Nto earn a badge before it's invented.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.90,0:01:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-[gasps] There should be a badge for that.\N-[gulps]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-[thuds]\N-[Frida screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-Frida?\N-[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilda!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[shouting]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Flipping head lamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.91,0:02:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,At least the last thing I ever did\Nwas be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[exhales]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sorry, Warren.\N-[doorbell rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.79,0:02:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[David's mum]\NDavid, your friends are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,First order of business: bug check.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Bug check complete.\NNow what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We could ride bikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.27,0:02:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Too boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why ride bikes\Naround the same old streets
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,when there's a great big world out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much we've never seen,\Nso much we don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's mystery everywhere you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,0:02:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, who's that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And what dastardly scheme\Nhas she been up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just some new girl on our street.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but what's her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha! See? She's a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilda, when you lived in the wilderness,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:03:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you knew everyone\Nbecause it was just you and your mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But here in Trolberg,\Nthere's a lot of people we don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you,\Nthere's something odd about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always alone.\NShe never talks to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen her go into a shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] Have you noticed\Nthe more you talk about how odd she is,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the more odd you sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.23,0:03:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just a teenager.\NMost teenagers are a bit weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So? People think elves are weird,\Nbut they're actually quite fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Alfur's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest are rather dull and tedious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, she moves fast\Nfor someone who walks so slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah! How'd she do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You said yourself, teenagers are weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is getting too spooky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just go to the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You scare awful easy for someone\Nwho's always got a bug on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm a bit jumpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:03:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably on account\Nof having nightmares all week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All week?\NWhat do you think is causing them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, don't take this the wrong way,\Nbut... you, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always dragging us\Nto see something weird
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,or telling us\Nabout some creepy thing you read,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,like how Trolberg has so many rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And that they get their tails tangled up\Nand become the fearsome Rat King.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I had a nightmare about rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, David.\NI didn't mean to scare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did you call it "fearsome"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with "fearsome"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to worry.\NI'll help rid you of your nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-How?\N-We're going to find the Rat King!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-[distant boat horn blaring]\N-[seagulls screeching]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[David] How is this meant to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hilda] The best way to overcome\Nyour fears is to face them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Like trolls. When you actually meet one,\Nyou realize they're not scary at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not that scary,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,except when you're staring\Ninto that giant, drooly troll mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and consider\Nthey could eat you in one bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,At least I know\Nwhat my next nightmare will be about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you've seen enough scary things,\Nyou don't get scared anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one of the perks\Nof being an adventurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-Come on.\N-[gulps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[David whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just like my nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Less scary in real life, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-[rumbling]\N-Uh, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[all screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming] Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ah! Ooh.\N-[screaming, grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[exhales]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[spits, clears throat]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] See? There was something\Nto be frightened about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:05:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but it wasn't rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in a way, we're both right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[stammering] Ra-- Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-What is it, David?\N-Ra-- Ra--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[rumbling]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rat King] Ah, visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you secrets to trade\Nwith the Rat King?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Secrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the keepers of all secrets\Nrats overhear from humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and we always wanna hear more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you secrets to trade?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose the polite thing\Nwould be to tell him a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we are guests in his home.\NWho's got a good one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[both whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-[whispering]\N-Uh-huh, uh-huh. Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, yes! Fascinating!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We never would have guessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:07:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What a delicious secret!\NOh! [laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And have we got a good one for you.\N[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The one responsible\Nfor your friend's nightmares
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is the teenage girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The one walking around the neighborhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-I knew there was something off about her.\N-[Rat King laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we're so bad!\NNo pudding for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[cackling]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] He's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[crickets chirping]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[electricity buzzing]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-[static crackles]\N-Frida, do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-Over.\N-I'm in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Hilda, how could this girl\Nbe causing David's nightmares?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-Over.\N-I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why this time,\Nwe cannot lose her. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[shouting]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Bertrand.\NI'm not myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Frida, something's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see anything? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[zaps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] She's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,David, get in position. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She was just here, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Twig!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[doorknob rattles]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[David over radio] Target acquired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Way down at the end\Nof Nutten Avenue, turning left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[thuds]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I just remembered\NI'm terrified of heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[Frida] Hilda!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-[tires screech]\N-Get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I've got a helmet for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly, we're losing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Twig's got her scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's headed for the Huldrawood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-Yeah, she can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay, Twig.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilda, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're so close.\NWe can't stop now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean,\Naccording to the Sparrow Scout manual,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you really ought to use a bowline knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:09:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[girls giggling]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And as David's head fell off his body\Nand tumbled screaming down the rocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,he realized his head was bouncing\Ndirectly into the mouth of another troll!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[girls laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.93,0:10:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing] That's too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen here, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.\NThat was eerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.64,0:10:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I-- I mean, I'm not scared,\Nbut I can see how you'd think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[David groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She told my nightmares to her friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I deserve a royalty or something.\NDon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But first, we need to find out\Njust what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[thuds]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you'll find that book\Nto be of interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hilda] "Tales of the Marra."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"The marra are nightmare spirits\Nwho are said to haunt the Huldrawood."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, that's them all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How did the librarian know exactly\Nwhat book we needed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's her job, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It says here that the marra\Nvisit sleeping humans at night
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and create nightmares out of their fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm not just having nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also an evil spirit in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I felt better\Nbefore you started helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, David.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It says here the marra will pass over you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,if you strap yourself into bed\Nwith a leather belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No good.\NI am deathly afraid of belts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckily, it's never been a problem
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,since I'm very good\Nat fitting into trousers just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Belting yourself into bed\Nis no way to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have to talk with this marra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to settle this\Nonce and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[David] Well, Hilda is going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to bed early\Nas soon as Hilda leaves,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,which she is doing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[door closes]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's no bug on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, never mind.\NGood for you, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[Twig squeaks]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[trills softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting, gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mum] Hilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a bug on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you picked it up\Nfrom that David kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You were right,\Nthat bowline knot is fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. And your story worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother thinks\NI'm sleeping over at your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.\NHere's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sleep in David's bed\Nso the marra will think I'm David.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll hide under David's desk\Nwhere the marra won't see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to make sure the marra\Ndoesn't go after you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll belt yourself\Ninto the sleeping bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the marra always enter\Nthrough the keyhole,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so Alfur will guard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,According to Alfur's records,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the marra has no paperwork on file\Nwith the elves,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so she won't see him when she comes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[bones crack]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hilda] Alfur will wake you up,\Neven though you can't see him, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[whispers] Frida!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hilda] You'll use the marra's weakness,\Nthe leather belt,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to hold her in place\Nlong enough for us to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-[screams]\N-Dream on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I'm gonna let myself get trapped\Nby some little kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh?\N-Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[both grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that crazy girl\Nwho's been chasing me all over town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're the one who's been giving\Nmy friend David nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, duh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His nightmares are the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much to work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He is scared of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:14:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, whatever. You like scaring him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rat King told me David was, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,practically crying\Nwhen you went to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the Rat King?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to help David\Nget over his fears,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you're just making them worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I want you to leave David alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.\NThe girls love his nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not giving that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you pick on David\Nbecause it's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet your friends\Nare secretly laughing at you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,for not stepping up your nightmare game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-Excuse me?\N-Don't you think they'd be more impressed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,with a nightmare\Nfrom someone harder to scare?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.01,0:15:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Like who? You?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you're afraid of a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Go to sleep, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see\Nwhose nightmare game is on point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take your best shot...\Nif you promise to leave David alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.07,0:15:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you wake her up before I'm done,\Nthe deal's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[gulps] Got it. Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sleep tight.\N-Oh, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna sleep so tight, you won't\Nbelieve how... tight I'm going to s-sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hilda groaning, growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-Well?\N-[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not easy falling asleep\Non purpose, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-[snoring continues]\N-[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[Twig whines]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.54,0:16:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[yawns] Is that Hilda snoring?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[both screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[clock ticking]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:17:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[snoring softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[yawns] Mum, are you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilda, you let the spiders in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Mum.\NI can use these for my bug collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll get a Sparrow Scout badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not frightened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.\NThey're cute in that ugly sort of way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[loud thud]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[roars]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[forest giant] Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:18:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll make a fine between-meals snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[snorts, roars]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Forest giants aren't known to eat people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying new things\Nbecause your life's in a rut?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating people won't fill that void.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoooaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-[woffs calling]\N-Hey, "whoaf" sounds a bit like "woff."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why we call you a "woff"?\NI bet it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What scares you, crazy girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But you must have a...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilda! Down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This way! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams] Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't ride woffs, we ride bikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NThe street hasn't got a woff lane, has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,W-- Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[tires screech]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilda, can't you ride a bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I can ride a bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[marra laughing, echoing]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! [panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my fault!\NI'm not from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[demonic voice] No, you're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, I guess she's not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:20:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming echoes]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[door opens]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where's Hilda?\N-[Frida] Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't wake Hilda,\Nor else David will keep having nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, though.\NUh, she's... she's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No! [grunts] Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hilda groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't make her do this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.46,0:21:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If she can handle them, then so can I.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hilda screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hilda! Wake up!\N-[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilda, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You were crying out in your sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,An adventurer\Nnever cries out in her sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, but what are you doing\Nin David's bedroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.53,0:21:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[birds chirping]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum wants me to stay close to home\Nfor a couple of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.83,0:21:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry you had to wake me.\NDid you have a nightmare again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, no.\NSweet dreams all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Literally about sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-The marra didn't come back?\N-[marra] Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no fun giving nightmares to someone\Nwho's brave enough to ask for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:21:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[exhales] About my secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the Rat King, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.40,0:22:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We trade each other's secrets on the reg.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.15,0:22:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[Frida] What secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, it... it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.07,0:22:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But it did remind me\Nthat seeing as I don't really know
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,how things work around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm awfully lucky\Nto have you two as friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, from now on, I won't force you to do\Nanything scary you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.92,0:22:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But we do want to.\NWe like that about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Y-- You, too, David?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.76,0:22:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I don't mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.34,0:22:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as I get\Nto have dreams about sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, got any new adventures planned?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.51,0:22:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it's not too boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.89,0:22:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you want to teach me how to ride a bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music playing]
